</item><item>
  <title>The long winter ahead</title>
  <description><![CDATA[
                <img src="http://esa.int/var/esa/storage/images/esa_multimedia/images/2013/03/the_long_winter_ahead/12592012-17-eng-GB/The_long_winter_ahead_small.jpg" width="170" height="96" align="left" hspace="8" /><br />
    <p>
Secluded from civilisation and living in a white desert, the crew at the Concordia research base in Antarctica have settled in to their home and are ready for the cold, long winter ahead.
</p>
  ]]></description>
  <link>http://esa.int/Our_Activities/Human_Spaceflight/Concordia/The_long_winter_ahead</link>
  
  <guid isPermaLink="false">fcdc6b8c8c221b9a2ffcab62969f6633</guid>
